Nowy Folwark  is a settlement in the administrative district of Gmina Parchowo, within Bytów County, Pomeranian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north of Parchowo,  north-east of Bytów, and  west of the regional capital Gdańsk.
For details of the history of the region, see History of Pomerania.
